  <description><![CDATA[<p>Ideally situated in the Bruyères suburb of <a data-udi="umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8}" title="Les Menuires">Les Menuires</a>, the Résidence Adonis offers high standard, self-catered accommodation with the ability to ski back virtually to the door.</p>
<h2>Self catered ski apartments</h2>
<p>These apartments have everything you need for a hassle free stay in the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys</a>. The apartments vary in size, however are an excellent choice for a group of friends or family travelling to France this winter season - each apartment has a well equipped kitchenette, lounge area with TV and you can opt to have an apartment with a bath for that touch of comfort. There's a fully stocked supermarket just opposite the residence, as well as a good choice of restaurants within a few minutes' walk. </p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>These apartments have a great location in Les Menuires, a short walk to the Bruyères gondola gives you access to the extensive Three Valleys ski area is easy, you certainly wont be short of areas to explore. The resort centre is nearby so you can stock up on the essentials at the supermarket or enjoy a meal out at one of the many restaurants available. </p>
<h2>Soothing spa and swimming pool</h2>
<p>After a day on the slopes, make the most of the indoor pool and wellness area available at the residence. If it is just too snowy to go skiing, or you want to entertain the family after a day on the slopes have a dip in the pool or soothe any aches in the sauna and steamroom.</p>]]></description>
