  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One Bedroom &amp; Alcove Apartments with shower</strong> are around 40m² sleeping two to four people with a double bedroom and twin beds in an alcove separated by a curtain.</p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom &amp; Alcove Apartments with bath </strong>are around 40m² sleeping four to six people with a double or twin bedroom, an alcove with twin beds separated by a curtain and pull out sofa beds in the lounge.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom apartments</strong> are around 48m² sleeping four to six people with two twin or double bedrooms, a pull out sofa beds in the living area, bathroom and two WCs</p>
<p><strong>Three Bedroom Apartments</strong> are around 60m² sleeping six to eight people with three twin or double bedrooms, a pull out sofa beds in the living area, bathroom, shower room and two WCs</p>
<p>Please note that in some two or three bedroom apartments, the second bedroom can sometimes be an alcove separated by a curtain. Beds made on arrival except sofa beds and a cleaning kit provided - end of stay cleaning is not included, and can be arranged locally for an additional fee.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchenette with microwave/ grill, hob, fridge and dishwasher</li>
<li>Lounge area</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Bathroom and WC</li>
<li>DVD players are available on request</li>
<li>One linen set with towels per person per week</li>
<li>Baby cots are available (on request)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
